---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
    body-class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-white text-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200"
    ,
    header-navbar-class="sticky top-0 z-20 w-full flex-none"
>
    <section class="space-y-4">
        <div
            class="mx-auto items-center bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 pt-48 pb-40 text-center"
        >
            <h1
                class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold tracking-wide text-white uppercase md:text-6xl"
            >
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
        </div>
        <div
            class="mx-auto flex max-w-(--breakpoint-xl) flex-wrap gap-2 pl-4 text-sm text-gray-400 [&>span:not(:last-child)]:after:mx-2 [&>span:not(:last-child)]:after:content-['|']"
        >
            <span>Updated: March 16, 2026</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main
        class="mx-auto flex max-w-(--breakpoint-xl) flex-1 flex-col justify-center space-y-8 px-4 py-4 md:space-y-12 lg:py-8"
    >
        <p class="text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            This Privacy Policy explains what information may be collected through this website, how
            it is used, and how it is protected. By using this website or submitting a message
            through the contact form, you acknowledge the practices described in this policy.
        </p>

        <article class="policy space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Information Collected
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    This website collects very limited personally identifiable information, which
                    may include:
                    <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 py-2 pl-4 text-lg text-body md:py-4">
                        <li>Name</li>
                        <li>Email address</li>
                        <li>Message content</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    This information is voluntarily provided by you when you submit the contact
                    form. No other personal information is intentionally collected.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Purpose of Data Collection
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    The information you provide through the contact form is used solely for the
                    purpose of: responding to your message and/or communicating with you regarding
                    your inquiry Your information will not be used for marketing purposes, shared
                    with third parties for advertising, or sold.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    How the Information Is Processed
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    Contact form submissions are processed using Netlify Forms, a service provided
                    by
                    <span class="font-semibold text-heading underline decoration-brand"
                        >Netlify, Inc</span
                    >. When you submit the form, the information you provide is securely transmitted
                    and stored by Netlify in order to deliver the message. You can learn more about
                    Netlify’s privacy practices here: <a
                        href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/"
                        class="text-fg-brand hover:underline">https://www.netlify.com/privacy</a
                    >
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Data Retention
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    Personal information submitted through the contact form is retained only for as
                    long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and maintain relevant
                    correspondence. Information may be deleted periodically when it is no longer
                    required.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Data Security
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    Reasonable measures are taken to protect submitted information. The website uses
                    secure HTTPS connections, and form submissions are processed through Netlify’s
                    infrastructure. However, no method of transmission over the internet can be
                    guaranteed to be completely secure.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Rights of Data Subjects
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) applicable
                    within the European Economic Area (EEA), individuals whose personal data is
                    processed (data subjects) may have certain rights regarding their personal
                    information. Depending on your location and applicable laws, you may have the
                    right to:
                    <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 py-2 pl-4 text-lg text-body md:py-4">
                        <li>
                            Request <span
                                class="font-semibold text-heading underline decoration-brand"
                                >access</span
                            > to the personal information you have provided.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request <span
                                class="font-semibold text-heading underline decoration-brand"
                                >correction</span
                            > of inaccurate or incomplete information.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request <span
                                class="font-semibold text-heading underline decoration-brand"
                                >deletion</span
                            > of your personal information when it is no longer necessary for the purposes
                            for which it was collected.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    If you wish to exercise any of these rights, you may contact the website owner
                    using the contact form available on this website. Requests will be handled in
                    accordance with applicable data protection regulations.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Third-Party Services
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    This website uses Netlify to process form submissions. Aside from this service,
                    no third-party services are used to collect personal information through the
                    contact form. Additional third-party services may apply if other tools are added
                    to the website in the future.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Changes to This Policy
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect changes to the
                    website or legal requirements. Updates will be published on this page with the
                    revised date.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">
                    Contact
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or the handling of your
                    data, you may get in touch through the contact form available on this website.
                </p>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
